// src/pages/commercial/washer-repair/coin-laundry-repair.astro
// Phase B-5/2 — Coin/vended laundry sub-service. SEO money page: 100 vol, KD 4, $350 CPC.
// Brands: Speed Queen + Huebsch + Maytag Commercial + Continental Girbau Vended.
