    q: "What's the vandalism repair scope?",
    a: "Common vandalism repairs: door glass cracking (front-load doors are tempered glass, $360 to $640 replacement), control panel damage, coin slot tampering, drain pipe disconnection. We handle all of these. For repeated vandalism in high-incidence locations, we discuss hardening options (reinforced control covers, security cameras integration, anti-tamper coin slots).",
  },
  {
    q: "Do you do multi-location service contracts for laundromat chains?",
    a: "Yes. Multi-location chains often use scheduled-maintenance contracts: quarterly preventive service across all units, plus emergency dispatch on demand. Contract pricing reduces per-visit cost and prioritizes the chain in dispatch scheduling. Contact us for chain-account pricing.",
  },
  {
    q: "What's your warranty?",
    a: "90 days SDAR labor warranty on every repair. Brand component warranties (Alliance Laundry, Whirlpool, Continental Girbau) processed separately. BHGS #A49573, CSLB C-20 plus C-38, EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410, BBB A+.",
  },
];

