        <h3>Koreatown laundromat, Speed Queen ZWN432 30 lb top-load</h3>
        <p>Coin slot jammed (foreign object) plus drain pump showing reduced flow (heavy lint accumulation). Cleared coin mechanism, replaced drain pump, deep-cleaned drain hose. Total: $120 plus $440 drain pump plus $80 coin slot service = $640.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-card">
        <h3>San Fernando Valley multi-location chain, Huebsch HC30 30 lb front-load</h3>
