      </div>
      <div class="story-card">
        <h3>East LA single-location laundromat, Speed Queen SF35 35 lb front-load</h3>
        <p>Door interlock switch failed (5-year unit, heavy use) plus belt drive frayed. Single-visit replacement of both. Total: $120 plus $260 interlock plus $340 belt = $720.</p>
      </div>
