    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> on-premise hotel and hospital laundry on this page (see <a href="/commercial/washer-repair/on-premise-laundry-repair/">OPL repair</a>); industrial contract laundry on this page (see <a href="/commercial/washer-repair/industrial-laundry-repair/">industrial laundry repair</a>); residential laundry (see <a href="/services/washer-repair/">residential washer repair</a>); coin mechanism manufacture or coin-supply service (specialty trade); building-level plumbing work (specialty plumbers).</p>
